Directed by Vipul Amrutlal Shah

Written by Ritesh Shah

Cast Parineeti Chopra (Jasmeet Kaur). Arjun Kapoor (Param). Satish Kaushik (Gurnaam). Hiten Patel (Immigrant). Shreya Mehta (Alisha). Abhimanue Kamboj ((as Abhimanue)).Katie Iqbal. Aditya Seal (Sam). Manoj Anand (Boat Immigrant). Anil Charanjeett (Iqbal (as Anil Mange)). Jitendra Rai (Immigrant (as Jitendra Kumar)). Atul Sharma (Immigrant). Bharat Mistri (Wedding Suit Boutique Owner). Sammy Jonas Heaney (Dancer (as Sammy John Heaney)). Raj Awasti (Immigrant). Alankrita Sahai (Alisha). Kishore Bhatt (Mosque Goer). Rene Costa (Chris The Boss).Abhimanue Kamboj. Vaunisha Kapoor (Club Goer). Anjum Batra (Gurpreet Singh). Glenn Webster (Security / Party Guest). Vinod Nagpal (Sam’s Grandfather). Paul Blackwell (Police officer). Sonia Goswami (Posh Party Diner). Kevin Matadeen (Immigrant). Nicholas Benjamin (Party Guest (as Nicholas Benjamin (II)). Pratik Dixit (KG). Denis Michallet (French Policeman). Deepali Monga (Simmi). Hugo Nicolau (French Policeman). Adnan Malik (London Pedestrian). Alexander Szelle (Town Hall Shopper). Manish Kumar Srivastava (Shyam). Dash Jivram (Immigrant). Karl-Martin Rantapelkonen (Smuggler). Frina Mehta (Mean British Indian Girl). Umesh Wadhvani (Immigrant). Georgia Gill (Glamourous Party Goer / Airline Passenger). Raj & Pablo (Raj / Pablo). Jahir Islam (Raju). Kinjal (Posh Party Guest). Jay Gandhi (Jameel – Mosque Visitor). Shahan Chaudhry (London Pedestrian). Chirag N. Patel (Immigrant). Varnesh Sharma (Chai Wala). Navdeep Monga (Airport Travelier). Kuldeep N.(Posh Party Waitress / Posh Party Guest). Tindy C. Chaggar (Restaurant Customer). Jithu Paul (Lead Background Dancer (Bhare Bazaar)).Ammar Taalwala. Jashan Singh Arneja (Kuljeet). Vital Karia (Posh Party Diner).Usman Chauhan. Neha Pushp (Office Party Guest). Minhaz Zee (Rafiq). Gergo Baranyi (Passenger (uncredited))

Language Hindi

Producers Sameer Chopra. Jean-Patrick Costantini. Akshay Gada. Dhaval Gada. Kushal Gada. Karan Gill. Reshmaa Kadakia. Firuzi Khan. Ravichand Nallappa. Cyrus Patel. Aashin A. Shah. Vipul Amrutlal Shah. Adi Sharmaa

Production Blockbuster Movie Entertainer. Inesa Entertainmen. Namastey Production
